    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that\u2019s ready for all your adventures? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super well-loved and runs like a dream, making it the perfect companion for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It looks great and feels even better behind the wheel. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come by and take it for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2008 Porsche Cayman S. This mid-engine masterpiece is powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six engine, mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping and a limited-slip differential for superior corner exit traction. Maintenance is up to date, with focus on the cooling system and recent fluid services for the hydraulic steering and braking systems. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver status, the drivetrain remains tight with no signs of bore scoring or IMS issues. It sits on staggered 19-inch alloys wrapped in high-performance rubber, ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regular service history. Minor exterior scuffs. Mechanicals sound.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well are present\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show only light bolster wear, and all electronic features, including the premium sound system and navigation, function perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound, with a complete service history documenting regular oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts without hesitation. It sits on a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining, ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. With a balanced history of care and consistent servicing, it offers a refined driving experience and exceptional value for the discerning buyer.",
      "price": 36500.0,
