    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved? This beauty is ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smooth, and has plenty of life left in it. I've taken really good care of it, and it definitely shows. It's perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is equipped with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power distribution to the rear wheels. The chassis has been vetted with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings to maintain torsional rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains robust, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline and exceptional throttle response. Recent service includes valve clearances and a cooling system overhaul, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
